Class AeSchemaTime

All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeSchemaType, java.io.Serializable
public class AeSchemaTime
extends AeSchemaDateTime

This class represents a time as defined by the xsd:time datatype. An object of this type can be constructed from an xsd:time formatted string, or from a Date or Calendar java object.
